About This Product

This low-profile sectional sofa offers a cozy spot for lounging and relaxing, with its wide armrests that double as a surface for your laptop or magazines. Upholstered in soft corduroy in your choice of color, this sofa is designed to withstand scratches from pets, making it a great choice for family spaces. The back is cushioned with cotton fill, and the seat features pocket springs for added comfort. It even includes two accent pillows for extra support. You can easily adjust the sectional to an L-shape, a partitioned straight sofa, a sleeper sofa, or a twin sofa bed, accommodating various spaces such as your living room, lounge, home office, apartment, and more

Features

  • No Assembly Required: Enjoy your new sectional sofa immediately, just unbox it and relax with no assembly hassles
  • Pet-friendly fabric: Engineered to withstand the claws of pets, this soft fabric remains intact and looking new for longer periods
  • Generous Armrest: 11" wide thickened armrests provide ample relaxation space for your entire arm, which can be used as a pillow for lying down and resting for a moment
  • Comfortable and sturdy: Featuring flexible, high-quality pocket springs for enhanced support and durability, combined with brand new high-density foam for a resilient sitting experience
  • Warm Tip: The shipment includes two cartons with a compression package design. Upon receiving the goods, please open the package and gently pat the product to help it stretch out completely, leaving it for 72 hours will provide better seat height resilience. If your sofa arrives with wrinkles, please use a steam iron to iron it and try to use a thin cloth as a barrier to prevent the sofa from coming into direct contact with excessive heat
  • Please note that the fabric has a directional texture, which can create a slight variation in appearance depending on the angle of the light. In darker lighting conditions, it may appear more muted.
